data.description: ---WARNING--- You are about to walk into your new home and you will never want to leave. ABSOLUTELY STUNNING!!! You will NOT find a nicer, cleaner, more beautiful, more updated condo ANYWHERE!!! From the moment you enter 807 Gables Drive, you will be absolutely in love. This home seller has paid attention to every single detail. Kitchen and both Bathrooms have been completely redone. New countertops, freshly painted cabinets with updated hardware, new backsplash, new tile showers, new sinks. Hardwood Laminate flooring and Ceramic Tile grace every floor throughout the home. All new fixtures and hardware throughout. Lovely covered balcony that showcases a beautiful view of nature. NEW HVAC, NEW FURNACE, NEW WATER HEATER 2008. Honestly, you will fall in love with this one. Do not delay because this one will not last long, I promise!!! NOTE: Condo fee includes sewer, water, pest control, termite bond, garbage pickup, common grounds maintenance, all exterior maintenance, pool maintenance.
